  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Base Plan:</strong> All allied creatures within 30 feet of you gain Temporary hit points equal to half your Ninjutsu (or Genjutsu) ability score at the end of each of their turns. This lasts for a number of rounds equal to your Proficiency Bonus.</p><p><strong>Enhanced Plan:</strong> If a Brave order is used to enhance this plan allied creatures instead gain Temporary Hit points equal to your full Ninjutsu or Genjutsu ability score. When this plan is enhanced, you retain the effects of the base plan. You do not lose Temporary Hit points gained from this Plan when ending its effects. Temporary Hit Points are lost after 1 minute.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
